C++ extension library:

string.hpp	Robust copy-on-write thread-safe basic_string implementation.
sstream.hpp	basic_stringbuf implementation that uses advantages of
		reference counted basic_string.
format.hpp	Formatting of arguments according to printf-like format-string.

Additional files used by above headers:

atomic.hpp	Atomic exchange/add inline functions (system-dependent).
iosfwd.hpp	Forward declarations of ext::basic_stringbuf-related classes.
utility.hpp	Various utility functions and classes.
hash_map.hpp	Wrapper for vendor-supplied <hash_map> header (only gcc and
		msvc supported for now).
type_traits.hpp	Type traits template classes.

Ext library uses following Boost libraries:

    MPL
    call_traits
    type_traits
